snippet.title: The Alters | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add The Alters to your wishlist and stay updated:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1601570/The_Alters/

To survive on a lonely planet, Jan creates alternate versions of himself - the alters. Each alter’s personality is shaped by Jan’s various life paths. The Alters begs a simple question surrounding life-changing moments and the decisions people make: What if…?

Follow The Alters:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/altersgame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/altersgame

Also, Jan Dolski has an Instagram account!
https://www.instagram.com/jandolski
